{"tid":873290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慾男插金屬洞腫脹卡住　2周拔不出來險壞死","createTime":"2018-10-23T10:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T16:37:59.000Z","uid":121473,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aaaca7aa0a8eb3c32bdc7366ba08527b1988d389","tid":873290,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ejAVUCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FejAVUCP.jpg&h=bfa58414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫護人員發現A男的下體，竟然卡著2個「軸承」。翻攝CEN<br />\n<br />\n印度1名33歲的男子A，日前慾火中燒，偷偷將生殖器官塞入中央有洞的金屬機械零件「培林」（承軸，bearing，香港俗稱啤令）中，結果在摩擦獲得快感後，因生殖器官脹大，反而無法將這個金屬圈拿下來，造成下體持續疼痛和腫脹，但A男卻超有耐力，硬是卡了2周才就醫。<br />\n <br />\n根據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，印度新德里的德里大學聯盟醫院（UCMS &amp; GTB Hospital）醫護人員，發現A男的下體，竟然卡著2個「軸承」，並且是將生殖器底部壓住，血液無法順利回流到前端，造成該處組織開始出現壞死的跡象。<br />\n <br />\n報導中說，為了避免組織壞死擴散，醫護人員先給A男注射「消腫」藥物，又打算用醫療用線，將軸承割斷，但2種方法都失敗了，為了跟時間賽跑拯救GG，只好使用了專門切割大理石的「石材切割器」，來將金屬軸承切開。<br />\n <br />\n報導中說，醫護人員先是將A男全身麻醉，接著一邊用切割器切割，一邊還要向A男的生殖器官「沖冷水」，以避免切割時產生的熱能燒傷GG，最後成功解除了危機。<br />\n <br />\n報導中說，A男恢復十分良好，手術2周後也測試「功能正常」，醫師表示，還好A男沒有再拖下去，不然除了組織壞死之外，還可能會造成尿道損傷。<br />\n <br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181023/1452863/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181023%2F1452863%2F&d=aAnQvGgueqfulnl0CJc62i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=61dfd0d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181023%2F1452863%2F&h=1fd71df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181023/1452863/</a>"},{"pid":"ae48e55ea4e5a12cae0284d689c48e0560676aea","tid":873290,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"印度活塞男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2eaedc6003bf9e417dee78200fffba0e79fa1b","tid":873290,"uid":49853,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"扯足兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5311c4cb5035f7c991ed9f5ce6afa96dc23492a","tid":873290,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"兩星期都唔軟咁堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66679935d2f18ce07986d72a3292142cc347f8f","tid":873290,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d85bfe7396f1d007ea4f80b4c8bba0860eab72","tid":873290,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"想知佢點出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1e493f58d26849593cc37dc257b61c231b3fd9","tid":873290,"uid":97451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3490a01739abd694cf4591582bca7319d8b016e6","tid":873290,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1e493f58d26849593cc37dc257b61c231b3fd9","tid":873290,"uid":97451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"十年架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c95af778adac0f101cda3acc2a83285fd3acaa","tid":873290,"uid":52006,"like":9,"dislike":0,